<h1>Welcome to Business App</h1>
<p>This application has been upgraded from a console application to a web application. Choose from the following options:</p>

<h2>Available Operations:</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Reverse String</strong> - Reverses the characters in your input text</li>
    <li><strong>Remove Whitespace</strong> - Removes all spaces from your input text</li>
    <li><strong>Letter Pattern</strong> - Generates a pattern using letters based on number of rows</li>
    <li><strong>Star Pattern</strong> - Generates a diamond pattern using stars based on number of rows</li>
    <li><strong>Circle Area</strong> - Calculates the area of a circle from its radius</li>
    <li><strong>Prime Check</strong> - Checks if a number is prime</li>
</ul>

<p>Use the navigation menu above to access each operation.</p>